OverTheWire Bandit – Level 0 → Level 1

## Level Goal
The goal of this level is to log into the Bandit game server using SSH.

## SSH Details
- **Host:** bandit.labs.overthewire.org
- **Port:** 2220
- **Username:** bandit0
- **Password:** bandit0

## Command Used
```bash
ssh bandit0@bandit.labs.overthewire.org -p 2220
Steps
Open terminal.

Connect to the server using the SSH command above.

Enter the password when prompted.

Successfully logged in as bandit0.

Result
Login successful. Ready to move to Level 1.

What I Learned
How to use SSH

Connecting to a remote server using a custom port
